### BASE URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ============================
### Register a driver
### ============================

### Register Alice (near)
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 1.0,
    "longitude": 1.0
  }
}

###

### Register Bob (mid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 50.0,
    "longitude": 50.0
  }
}

###

### Register Charlie (far)
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 100.0,
    "longitude": 100.0
  }
}

###

### Missing name → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": {
    "latitude": 1.0,
    "longitude": 1.0
  }
}

###

### Missing location → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dave"
}

###

### Missing latitude → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dave",
  "location": {
    "longitude": 1.0
  }
}

### ============================
### Update driver location
### ============================

### Update Alice's location — replace {id} with real driver ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{aliceId}}/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": {
    "latitude": 50.0,
    "longitude": 50.0
  },
  "available": true
}

###

### Unknown driver → expect 404
PUT {{baseUrl}}/drivers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": {
    "latitude": 1.0,
    "longitude": 1.0
  },
  "available": true
}

### ============================
### Nearby drivers
### ============================

### Get 3 nearest drivers — expect Alice, Bob, Charlie in order
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/nearby?latitude=0&longitude=0&count=3

###

### Limit to 1 — expect only Alice
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/nearby?latitude=0&longitude=0&count=1

###

### Missing count → expect 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/nearby?latitude=0&longitude=0

###

### count=0 → expect 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/nearby?latitude=0&longitude=0&count=0